item.title: The Pros and Cons of VC Funding for AI Startups: A Review of the Crunchbase Megadeals Board
item.description: The Crunchbase Megadeals Board is a useful resource for traders and investors who want to keep track of the latest trends in VC funding for AI startups. This board tracks announced venture funding deals in 2023 of $100 million or more in the Crunchbase database that were raised by U.
